{"tid":1708061,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日只係個開始 為明天做好準備","createTime":"2019-11-11T12:51:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T14:04:41.000Z","uid":125224,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"089ba8b3e1c3ace29e6793f36efdecc952712c9e","tid":1708061,"uid":125224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:51:36.000Z","msg":"不完美可改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />黎明行動2.0<br />\n1. 真係堅持早少少起身 哨兵早少少踩線<br />\n今日各區大量出現便衣狗 哨兵提早踩線有助手足聚人<br />\n2. 快閃 Be water<br />\n手足set完rb 藍絲中途想搬走rb 街坊大大力屌 等手足set完可以盡快離去<br />\n手足都唔好戀戰 藍絲係抵屌 但你地有更重要既事要做 時限為5分鐘<br />\n3. 地點選擇<br />\n經過今日 某d關鍵路口 黨鐵 應該好早會有狗或者便衣狗守住 手足耐心等睇哨兵踩完點先行動<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不被捕</span> 關鍵路口封唔到可考慮快閃兩三個細路口去做同樣效果<br />\nTG group內可多建議不同重要既細路口 方便手足決定下一個行動目標<br />\n4. 保持距離<br />\n防守黎講 唔少片都證明遠攻有用<br />\n街坊撚狗都要保持距離 記住對方係癲狗黎 準時咬人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />知道旺角有手足仲打緊仗 但聽日行動就到 盡快做好討論 做更多宣傳比手足知道聽日可以點做<br />\n期待明天做緊更好 不被捕<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JHcXuoR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJHcXuoR.png&h=452ba5e1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"606f405b9ea8c5ac48591a0659d388e292ce13d2","tid":1708061,"uid":125224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T12:59:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c253351b729819f6a9d7ea19d5e3898a13e4600a","tid":1708061,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T13:00:17.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"dabacf16f2271c1475b05bc7e563911d321bfcd4","tid":1708061,"uid":125224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T13:01:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4ffb89fcb77114f61d1d6f2a0b478da47fbf414","tid":1708061,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT